2. iPad connects to your WiFi
3. Open Safari to the Pi's address
4. Enable Guided Access to lock it to that page
5. Configure refresh intervals and interactive/passive modes via the web interface

### Sustainability Impact
This approach lets people reuse:
- Old iPads collecting dust
- Retired Android tablets  
- Even old smartphones as displays
- Any device with a modern web browser

### Technical Feasibility
